data.description: Location, Location, Location, Come see this waterfront home located in a beautiful and peaceful neighborhood.  Three spacious bedrooms and 2.5 baths.  This two story home is unique and stunning with vaulted ceilings and an upstairs loft.  Fireplace, wet bar, screen porch, balcony, and boat dock are just a few of the numerous features of this home.  Cozy but contemporary.  The home has been well maintained and many major items have been updated and or remodeled.  This is a move in ready home. You will need to see this home to appreciate the serenity, charm, and roominess of this outstanding home.
